{"tid":1759043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得素人咁多先難比人收買","createTime":"2019-11-27T12:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T12:16:09.000Z","uid":193217,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef26604e4f347753e2d863cf407d0fb6895a34a7","tid":1759043,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:05:22.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得依家共產黨應該對保皇絕望<br />\n佢班人應該會成為condom.但你話依家中共<br />\n仲會搵到咩人去選而可以肯定win呢.我相信<br />\n中共自己都無呢個把握.反而呢把素人佢地<br />\n肯定會比中共mark實.所以呢班素人心真係要定<br />\n但中共要收買其實亦要左唸右唸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我亦開心咁多唔係政黨既人當選<br />\n因為一入政黨.佢地就會受到限制<br />\n但如果係素人呢.佢地就真係為選民負責<br />\n除非佢地唔想永續啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即使係民主派.你係唔係全相信呢<br />\n我唸無一個人會講100%相信<br />\n但點都好過班仆街保皇黨.搞到香港不能向前<br />\n咪9都唔做<br />\n<br />\n呢班素人未來會成為一個好龐大既政治力量<br />\n對依家日漸老化既香港係好重要<br />\n今次一次過踢撚走晒班老既.貪既保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未來呢班素人會成為下一批政治力量"},{"pid":"fd1fac3b5a1ba8a721a609a6256a8366600b8e9a","tid":1759043,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:06:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"79209bc8c2b99887ad257fb8f45ab8904a8097ac","tid":1759043,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:07:21.000Z","msg":"點睇民主黨有90個？"},{"pid":"2b2a83fab0a6e52518b13769e6540f1b275179de","tid":1759043,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79209bc8c2b99887ad257fb8f45ab8904a8097ac","tid":1759043,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:07:21.000Z","msg":"點睇民主黨有90個？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime